<paragraph id="F1C7879F9563622208ABC2E0CD8EFD37" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">
<emphasis id="B211E02BA88182471D9F04936EE9B844" bold="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Distribution.</emphasis>
This species is known only from the southeastern part of Bahia state (
<figureCitation id="9A6F0B4417D946CD6604E233C3C75372" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Known distribution of Solanum evolvuloides Giacomin &amp; Stehmann (triangles) along Rio de Contas (in grey) in the state of Bahia, Brazil." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/9960" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
